Class OrbPartitionProcess

java.lang.Object
  org.goldenorb.OrbPartitionProcess
All Implemented Interfaces:
PartitionProcess
public class OrbPartitionProcess
extends Object
implements PartitionProcess

OrbPartitionProcess is the OrbPartition process launcher. It sets the command-line arguments and output/error streams for each process.
